FREELY-DISTRIBUTABLE DEMO AVAILABLE

 A fully playable demo of Hired Guns is currently available on 
 ftp.wustl.edu (128.252.135.4) and will be appearing shortly on 
 all Aminet sites.
	
 DIRECTORY AND FILE NAME

 pub/aminet/game/demo/HiredGunsDemo.dms 

 HOW TO DECOMPRESS THIS DEMO

 Use the 'dms' command, which will write the data directly on to
 a disk in DF0:.  Type the following, and you will be prompted to
 insert a blank disk in the drive:

 1.> dms write HiredGunsDemo.dms

 DMS is available on Aminet:
 pub/aminet/util/arc/dms111.sfx (this archive will self-extract on
 execution)

